OL,3,CFather says he can't forgive the
OL,4,Cperson who threw acid in an unprovoked
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FA father-of-three from Thanet says he
OL,8,Fcan't forgive the person who threw
OL,9,Facid at him, in an unprovoked attack
OL,10,Fin Kent in February 2024.
OL,12,FPaul Atkins was targeted with a
OL,13,Fcorrosive substance as he walked
OL,14,Fthrough St Lawrence Churchyard in
OL,15,FRamsgate.
OL,17,FHe has been left with life-changing
OL,18,Fburns to his head and neck, but more
OL,19,Fthan a year later, his assailant has
OL,20,Fnot been found.
