OL,7,FA statement from Kent Police said: "On
OL,8,Fthe morning of Sunday 11 February
OL,9,F2024, a man reportedly had an
OL,10,Funidentified corrosive liquid thrown
OL,11,Fat him after he entered St Laurence
OL,12,FGraveyard, off Manston Road, Ramsgate.
OL,14,F"The victim was taken to the hospital
OL,15,Ffor treatment and was later discharged.
OL,17,F"A thorough investigation into the
OL,18,Fincident was carried out, during which
OL,19,Fa 22-year-old man from Ramsgate was
OL,20,Farrested on suspicion of assault.
